item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Kesha - iTunes LP extras ONLY
item.description:
Hi! i need help finding JUST the iTunes LP extra content.
iTunes LP version includes bonus music videos and photos.
i have the albums themselves already but i need the iTunes LP extra media content for these releases:
  • Animal + Cannibal https://web.archive.org/web/2014112.../animal-+-cannibal-deluxe-edition/id402692470
  • Cannibal https://web.archive.org/web/20140710023853/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cannibal/id402410451
  • Warrior (Deluxe) https://web.archive.org/web/2014070...m/us/album/warrior-deluxe-version/id582338179
theyll be in a folder that might look something like "album title - iTunes LP"
